description: This skill is triggered by utterances such as "stand up facts" or "comedian facts". This then prompts the user on whether they would like to receive their fact or quit. If they choose to receive their fact then one is randomly chosen from a pool of 15. Based off of the space geek template.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask stand up facts for comedian facts
Alexa, ask stand up facts for george carlin facts
name: Stand Up Facts
shortDescription: A skill that gives out short facts on stand up comedy
